messageBody:
Last year, I made the big switch from Windows to Mac OS X, and became a
Mac fanatic. I now regularly read Apple blogs. And whenever the Apple
Store website is down, everyone on these fan boy blogs actually gets
excited because it means Apple is about to release some cool new
products. Maybe www.junit.org is down for the same reason? :-)


Todd.
